## 8. Build Order Summary

| Phase | Name | Key Output |
|---|---|---|
| 1 | Foundation | Types, Skill/Research/Version services, IPC channels, 5 built-in skills |
| 2 | Skill Research Agent | Auto-generate skills via web search, SkillPicker UI |
| 3 | Planner Stage | Outline generation, outline editor UI, session setup |
| 4 | Generator Stage | Section-by-section writing, ghost text, cost badge |
| 5 | Reviewer + Surgical Edit | Reviewer flags, DiffViewer, paragraph fix, 3-pass limit |
| 6 | Research + Citations | Web research log, file upload, citation styles, fact-check |
| 7 | Version History + UX | Snapshot timeline, Zen mode, project isolation, keyboard-first |
| 8 | Settings + Distribution | Encrypted API keys, cost tracking, app packaging |

