## 9. All Design Decisions (Locked)

| Question | Decision |
|---|---|
| One model per project or per stage? | **One per project** (Q34B) |
| Research before or during loop? | **Before loop, manual** (Q14D) |
| How many reviewer passes? | **Max 3 auto, then ask user** (Q13B) |
| Planner vs Reviewer conflict? | **Planner wins** (Q12B) |
| Skill composability? | **Stack up to 3 with priority** (Q18B) |
| Citation style? | **User picks from APA/MLA/Chicago/etc.** (Q31D) |
| Pricing? | **Free, BYOK** (Q50E) |
| Distribution? | **Direct download, manual updates** (Q48A, Q49C) |
| Telemetry? | **None — 100% local** (Q46A) |
| Command palette? | **No — toolbar and menus** (Q44C) |
| Word count enforcement? | **Soft target — flag if >20% off** (Q15B) |
| Reviewer rewrite power? | **Flag + suggest, user decides** (Q11B) |
| Outline format? | **Hierarchical: sections → subsections → key points** (Q10B) |
| Edit display? | **Side-by-side diff (old vs new)** (Q25B) |
| Full rewrite allowed? | **Yes as fallback** (Q26A) |
| Formatting strategy? | **AI outputs Markdown → convert to TipTap** (Q27C) |
| Research log format? | **Structured entries + knowledge graph** (Q28 B+C) |
| Research mode? | **Auto by default, supervised for important docs** (Q29D) |
| Upload types? | **PDF, DOCX, TXT, PPTX slides** (Q30A) |
| Research persistence? | **Yes, cross-session** (Q32A) |
| Skill evaluation rubrics? | **Optional per skill** (Q20C) |
| Skill file location? | **User-accessible local dir + agent folder** (Q21B) |
| AI panel visibility? | **Toggleable, default visible** (Q40C) |
| AI suggestions in editor? | **Ghost text + highlighted blocks** (Q41 A+C) |
| Zen mode? | **Yes — editor + word count only** (Q42A) |
| Keyboard vs mouse? | **Equal — shortcuts + GUI** (Q43C) |
| Document continuity strategy? | **Rolling summary + neighboring paragraphs** (Q23 A+C) |
| Version history style? | **Snapshots at milestones, creative labels** (Q24B) |
| Skill built-in count? | **5 core, agent researches rest** (Q19A) |
